description: South Eastern and Eastern Europe Clearinghouse for the Control of Small Arms and Light Weapons: To further support the Stability Pact Regional Implementation Plan by building national and regional capacity to control and reduce the proliferation of SALW.

subproject.description: The development and implementation of well-designed, holistic and integrated SALW control, armed violence reduction and disarmament intervention programmes in South Eastern and Eastern Europe that contribute towards a reduction in illicit arms transfers, possession and armed violence and lead to an increase in stability and development.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
